{
  "chapter": "059",
  "title": "五宗世家",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "景帝诸子五母",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>共有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十三人</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>之子，母亲有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五人</span>，同母所生为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗亲</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>的儿子是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">荣（刘荣）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘德\">德（刘德）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘阏于\">阏于（刘阏于）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>的儿子是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘馀\">馀（刘馀）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘非\">非（刘非）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>。贾<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>的儿子是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胜\">胜（刘胜）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐姬</span>的儿子是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘发\">发（刘发）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span>的儿子是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘越\">越（刘越）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘寄\">寄（刘寄）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘乘\">乘（刘乘）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘舜\">舜（刘舜）</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "河间献王",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">河间</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：河间献王\">献王（河间献王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘德\">德（刘德）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>帝前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">河间</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。爱好<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒学</span>，一切行动都效法<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">儒者</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>地区的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸儒</span>多来跟从他交游。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "河间传嗣",
      "text": "在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：河间共王\">共王（河间共王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘不害\">不害（刘不害）</span>继位。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>后去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：河间刚王\">刚王（河间刚王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘基\">基（刘基）</span>代立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>后去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：河间顷王\">顷王（河间顷王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘授\">授（刘授）</span>代立。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "临江哀王",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临江</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：临江哀王\">哀王（临江哀王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘阏于\">阏于（刘阏于）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>帝前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临江</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>去世，无后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>为郡。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "栗太子被废",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临江</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：临江闵王\">闵王（临江闵王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">荣（刘荣）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇太子</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>，以故<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>身份为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临江</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "荣坐法自杀",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，因侵占庙外空地扩建宫室，皇上<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">征召</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">荣（刘荣）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">荣（刘荣）</span>出发，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北门</span>举行祭路神仪式。上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>后，车轴折断车废了。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江陵</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父老</span>流泪私下说：\"我们的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>不会回来了！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">荣（刘荣）</span>到了京城，到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>府受审。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郅都</span>责问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>恐惧，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。葬于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蓝田</span>。<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">燕</span>子<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万</span>衔土堆在坟上，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>都哀怜他。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "栗子皆无后",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘荣\">荣（刘荣）</span>最长，死后无后嗣，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，地入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南郡</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "栗姬三国",
      "text": "以上三国的开封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>之子。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "鲁共王馀",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>共<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘馀\">馀（刘馀）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮阳</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">被平定</span>后，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">改封</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。喜好修治<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宫室</span>、<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">苑囿</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>。晚年爱好音乐，不喜辞辩。为人口吃。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "鲁传嗣",
      "text": "在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘光\">光（刘光）</span>代为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。初好音乐车<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>；晚节吝啬，生怕财物不够。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "江都易王非",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">江都</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：江都易王\">易王（江都易王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘非\">非（刘非）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汝南</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘非\">非（刘非）</span>年<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十五</span>，有才力，上书请<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘非\">非（刘非）</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>后，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">改封</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">江都</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，治原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>国故地，因军功赐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旌旗</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元光</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>大举入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>为寇，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘非\">非（刘非）</span>上书请<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，皇上不许。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘非\">非（刘非）</span>喜好武力，修治<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宫观</span>，招揽四方<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪桀</span>，骄奢甚盛。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "江都建自杀",
      "text": "在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十六年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>后<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">衡山</span>谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>颇闻其谋。自认为国近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>，怕哪天他们起事，被吞并，就暗中制造<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">兵器</span>，时常佩其父所赐<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">印</span>，载<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗</span>出行。易<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>死未葬时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>看上了易<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>宠爱的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淖姬</span>，夜里派人把她迎到便殿里行奸。及至<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>案发，治罪党与牵连到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">江都</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>害怕，就派人带大量金<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>，想断其狱事。又信<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">巫祝</span>，派人祭祀妄言。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>又与其姊妹全都通奸。事既被举报，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公</span>卿请<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">捕</span>治<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘建\">建（刘建）</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>不忍，派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>就地讯问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>承认所犯，于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">自杀</span>。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，地入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广陵</span>郡。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "胶西于王端",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶西</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：胶西于王\">于王（胶西于王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">七国</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">被平定</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶西</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>为人凶戾，又阴痿，一接近<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>，就病<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">数月</span>。却爱幸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少年</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官。做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官的不久与后宫发生乱事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>擒<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>他，并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>其母子。屡犯国家<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>禁，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>屡请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>因<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>的缘故不忍，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>所为越甚。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>再请<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">削</span>其国，削去过半。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>心怀怨恨，于是不再理政理财。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">府库</span>坏漏净尽，财物腐烂损失以<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">巨万</span>计，终不收捡转运。下<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>官吏不得收租赋。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>尽撤卫队，封闭宫门，只从一门出游。屡次改名换姓，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布衣</span>装束，到其他郡国去。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "端杀二千石",
      "text": "相、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>前来上任的，奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>治理，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>总是找其过错告他，无罪者就诈以毒药<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>之。他用尽诈变手法，强到足以抵拒劝谏，智足以掩饰过错。相、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>如果顺从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>行事，则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>惩处。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶西</span>小国，而<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>伤<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>特别多。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "胶西国除",
      "text": "在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十七年</span>去世，终无儿子嗣后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，地入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">胶西郡</span>。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "程姬三国",
      "text": "以上三国开封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>之子。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "赵王彭祖",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广川</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘遂\">遂（刘遂）</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">被平定</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广川</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">改封</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十五年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>帝驾崩。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>为人巧佞卑谄，足恭而心深刻。好<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法律</span>，以诡辩中伤人。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>内宠姬妾和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>很多。相、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>想奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>治国，就会损害<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>家利益。所以每当相、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>到任，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>穿皂<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">布衣</span>，亲自迎接，安排<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>的住处，故意设种种疑问刺探，捕捉<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>的失言、触忌讳之处，随即记录下来。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>要想治事时，就用此要挟；不听，就上书告发，并以奸利事污蔑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>在位<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十馀年</span>，相、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>没有能满<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>的，总以罪去职，重的死，轻的<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">受刑</span>，所以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>没人敢治事。而<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>专擅大权，派人就地向县里的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">贾人</span>征收市场税，所得多于国家正式的租税。因此<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>家中金<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">钱</span>众多，但所赐姬妾<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸子</span>也花销殆尽。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>娶原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">江都</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：江都易王\">易王（江都易王）</span>的宠姬<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王建</span>盗来与之奸乱的<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">淖姬</span>为姬，非常宠爱。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "彭祖巡察邯郸",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>不喜修治<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宫室</span>、祭祀求福，好做吏事。上书请监督国中<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">盗贼</span>。常夜晚带着<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">走卒</span>巡行<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>街市。各过往使者宾客因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘彭祖\">彭祖（刘彭祖）</span>阴险邪僻，都不敢滞留<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "太子丹被废",
      "text": "他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘丹\">丹（刘丹）</span>与其女儿及同胞姐姐乱伦，与宾客<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">江充</span>有隙。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：江充\">充（江充）</span>告发<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘丹\">丹（刘丹）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘丹\">丹（刘丹）</span>因此被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>改<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "中山靖王胜",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：中山靖王\">靖王（中山靖王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胜\">胜（刘胜）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>帝驾崩。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘胜\">胜（刘胜）</span>为人嗜酒好色，有子嗣及亲属<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百二十馀人</span>。常与哥哥<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>互相指责，说：\"兄长为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，专门代替官吏理事。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>者应该每日听音乐声色。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>也反讥他说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>整日淫乐，不辅助<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>安抚<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，怎配称为藩臣！\""
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "中山传嗣",
      "text": "在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四十二年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：中山哀王\">哀王（中山哀王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘昌\">昌（刘昌）</span>继立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘昆侈\">昆侈（刘昆侈）</span>代为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "贾夫人二子",
      "text": "以上二国开封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>都是贾<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夫人</span>之子。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "长沙定王发",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：长沙定王\">定王（长沙定王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘发\">发（刘发）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘发\">发（刘发）</span>的母亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐姬</span>，原是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>的侍女。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>侍寝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>恰有月事，不愿前往，就装扮侍女<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐姬\">唐兒（唐姬）</span>代她夜间进御。皇上醉了不知，以为是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>而宠幸了她，遂有身孕。事后才知不是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">程姬</span>。等生下儿子，因此取名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘发\">发（刘发）</span>。在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>前<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。因其母卑微，不受宠，所以封在卑湿贫瘠之国。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "长沙传嗣",
      "text": "在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十七年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：长沙康王\">康王（长沙康王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘庸\">庸（刘庸）</span>继立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘鲋鮈\">鲋鮈（刘鲋鮈）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "唐姬一国",
      "text": "以上一国开封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐姬</span>之子。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "广川惠王越",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广川</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：广川惠王\">惠王（广川惠王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘越\">越（刘越）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">广川</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "广川王齐",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘齐\">齐（刘齐）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘齐\">齐（刘齐）</span>有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桑距</span>。后犯罪，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：桑距\">距（桑距）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：桑距\">距（桑距）</span>逃走，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>就<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">擒</span>拿他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗族</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：桑距\">距（桑距）</span>怨<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，就上书告<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘齐\">齐（刘齐）</span>与其姊妹通奸。从此之后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘齐\">齐（刘齐）</span>屡次上书告发<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公卿</span>及<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">幸臣</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">所忠</span>等。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "胶东康王寄",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：胶东康王\">康王（胶东康王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘寄\">寄（刘寄）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二十八年</span>去世。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>谋<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘寄\">寄（刘寄）</span>隐约听到其谋划，私下造楼<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">镞矢</span>作战守之备，观望<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>起事。等官吏追究<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">淮南</span>事，牵连到他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘寄\">寄（刘寄）</span>于皇上最亲近，心中伤愧，发病而死，不敢立后嗣，上报朝廷。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘寄\">寄（刘寄）</span>有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长子</span>名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贤\">贤（刘贤）</span>，母亲不受宠；<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>名<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘庆\">庆（刘庆）</span>，母亲宠爱，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘寄\">寄（刘寄）</span>常想立他，因不合次序，又有过失，终未提及。皇上怜他，就以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贤\">贤（刘贤）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>奉康<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后嗣，而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘庆\">庆（刘庆）</span>于原<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">衡山</span>故地，为六安<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "胶东哀王贤",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贤\">贤（刘贤）</span>在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十四年</span>去世，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">谥</span>为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：胶东哀王\">哀王（胶东哀王）</span>。其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘庆\">庆（刘庆）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "30": {
      "title": "六安王庆",
      "text": "六安<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘庆\">庆（刘庆）</span>，在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元狩</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：胶东康王\">康王（胶东康王）</span>之子身份为六安<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "31": {
      "title": "清河哀王乘",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">清河</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：清河哀王\">哀王（清河哀王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘乘\">乘（刘乘）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">清河</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>去世，无后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">国除</span>，地入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">清河郡</span>。"
    },
    "32": {
      "title": "常山宪王舜",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">常山</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：常山宪王\">宪王（常山宪王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘舜\">舜（刘舜）</span>，在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝景</span>中<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇子</span>身份封为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">常山</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘舜\">舜（刘舜）</span>最亲，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">少子</span>，骄横怠慢多行淫乱，屡犯禁令，皇上常宽宥。在位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三十二年</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">代立</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "33": {
      "title": "常山嫡孽之争",
      "text": "起初，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：常山宪王\">宪王（常山宪王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘舜\">舜（刘舜）</span>有不爱的姬妾生下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长男</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>因母亲无宠，也不得宠于<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩</span>生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>内嬖众多，所宠姬妾生子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘平\">平（刘平）</span>、子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘商\">商（刘商）</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后很少得宠。等宪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>病重，各宠姬妾<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">常</span>侍护病，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后也因妒忌不<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">常</span>侍护病，动辄回自己屋舍。医生进药，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>不亲尝药，又不宿于侍病处。及<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>薨，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>才到。宪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>平素不把<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>看作家人，薨时，也不分给财物。有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>官劝<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">令</span>众子与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>共分财物，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后不听。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>代立后，又不收恤<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>怨<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">使者</span>视察宪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>丧事，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>自言宪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>病时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后、<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>不侍奉，及薨，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">六天</span>就搬出居室，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>私下奸乱，饮酒，博戏，击<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">筑</span>，与女子驰车，环城过市，入牢狱看囚犯。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骞</span>核验<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后及讯问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>，请<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">逮</span>捕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>同奸的见证人，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>又藏匿他们。官吏追捕<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>十分紧急，派人施加鞭笞，擅自放出<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝所疑囚者。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>宪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩</span>及<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>。皇上因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩</span>素无善行，使<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘棁\">棁（刘棁）</span>陷之罪，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>又没有好的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">师傅</span>，不忍<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>请<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">脩</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">迁</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span>以家属居处<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">房陵</span>，皇上允准。"
    },
    "34": {
      "title": "分封真定泗水",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘勃\">勃（刘勃）</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>位<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">数月</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">迁</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">房陵</span>，国绝。过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">一个多月</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>因他最亲，就诏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">常山</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：常山宪王\">宪王（常山宪王）</span>早死，后妾不和，嫡庶相争，陷于不义以致<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>国，朕很怜悯。封宪<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘平\">平（刘平）</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万户</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真定</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>；封子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘商\">商（刘商）</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万户</span>，为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">泗水</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。\""
    },
    "35": {
      "title": "真定王平",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真定</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘平\">平（刘平）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">常山</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：常山宪王\">宪王（常山宪王）</span>之子为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">真定</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "36": {
      "title": "泗水思王商",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">泗水</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：泗水思王\">思王（泗水思王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘商\">商（刘商）</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元鼎</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">四年</span>以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">常山</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：常山宪王\">宪王（常山宪王）</span>之子为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">泗水</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>去世，其子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：泗水哀王\">哀王（泗水哀王）</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘安世\">安世（刘安世）</span>继立。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十一年</span>去世，无子。于是皇上怜<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">泗水</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>绝嗣，就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘安世\">安世（刘安世）</span>的弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘贺\">贺（刘贺）</span>为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">泗水</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "37": {
      "title": "兒姁六王",
      "text": "以上四国开封<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王夫人</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span>之子。此后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>又增封其支子为六安<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">泗水</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>二国。凡<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>，到如今共六<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>。"
    },
    "38": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>时<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都自收赋税，可自行任免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">内史</span>以下官员，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>只为他们设置<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>，用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄金印</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>自行任免<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉正</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，比拟<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>。自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">反</span>后，五宗<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>世，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>为他们设置<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">二千石</span>，去掉\"丞相\"称号，改称\"相\"，用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">银印</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>只能收食租税，被夺了权力。其后<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>中贫者甚至乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">牛车</span>。"
    },
    "39": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "景帝<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十三</span>子，五<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗亲</span>和睦。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">栗姬</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">废</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">临江</span>折轴。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘阏于\">阏于（刘阏于）</span>早薨，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">河间</span>儒服。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘馀\">馀（刘馀）</span>好宫苑，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：刘端\">端（刘端）</span>事驰逐。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">江都</span>有才，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">中山</span>享福。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">长沙</span>地小，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">胶东</span>造镞。 仁贤者继，悖乱者<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">族</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">兒姁</span>四<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">王</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">分封</span>为六。"
    }
  }
}